T1  - Are zero-Covid policies optimal?
AU  - Abel, Andrew B.
AU  - Panageas, Stavros
JO  - Review of Economic Dynamics
VL  - 53
SP  - 47
EP  - 70
PY  - 2024
DA  - 2024/07/01/
